Uko ufata isanamu kwose navyo bifise insiguro kandi n’inyishu ku bibazo mu nkuru yawe.Ufatiye ku burorero buzwi, igice kimwe kimwe ku kindi bifatanye bitanga inkuru ikwiye
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_3::cho: Ha agaciro abantu, ivyo bariko barakora naho bariko barabikorera.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_14: Ntimwibagire : Murabona ireresi ikozwe n’amafaranga menshi ariko ukabona isanamu ijugumira.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_12: Haraho amasanamu aba ari nico yerekana neza cinyegeje mu masanamu menshi kandi cakamaro.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_8:: Isanamu yo hagati na hagati ifasha mu gufata umuntu umwe canke babiri ariko ntibarenga.Izo sanamu zifasha kwerekana ingene ibihimba vy’umubiri w’umuntu biriko birakora.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_0:: Muri iki cigwa muraja kumenya ingene batera inkuru ifise amasanamu atandukanye.Amasanamu ya mbere umuntu akenera kugira atere inkuru.Ingene STORY MAKER ikoresha ayo masanamu.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_1::
![Akarorero k’isanamu yagutse](2.png) 
isanamu nziza itanga inkuru yumvikana.Isanamu yose ifashwe yama iri nico itemera.Isanamu yagutse yama ariyo ifasha mu gutunganya inkuru neza.Izo sanamu zifatirwa kure.Uko gufatirwa kure bituma n’ibindi biri mu micungararo yicukeneye navyo nyene bifasha mu kumenya inkuru neza.
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_1::cho: Isanamu nziza zose zafashwe neza zama zifise umumaro mu nkuru.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_4:: Izo sanamu zerekana aho ibintu biriko birabera zikoreshwa nkarimwe mu nkuru.Mukoresheje amasanamu yagutse mukerekana ubudasa buboneka cane bw’imwe n’iyindi mu gihe mugiye murazitondeka neza.
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_2::que: Nshika kuki kw’isanamu imwimwe yose nafashe ?
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_1::cho: Tanga ico ugomba gushikako kw’isanamu imwimwe yose.
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_6:: Amasanamu afashwe muri rusangi yerekana ingene abantu bariko barakora nivyo bariko barakora.
videos_different_shots::title: Ubwoko butandukanye bw’amasanamu
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_13: Amasanamu ya STORY MAKER afise ivyo yisangije.Agabuye ku buryo akoreshwa mu nkuru.Isanamu yerekana ikintu; umuntu n’ico avuga wenyene
videos_different_shots::markdown_card_10: Isanamu nini nayo iba itumbereye umuntu, n’ibigumbagumba vyiwe.Shingira ku maso yiwe gusa hama werekane ibigumbagumba vyiwe.
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_1::que: Ntegerezwa kumenya ko isanamu zanje zatotse.
videos_different_shots::quiz_card_3::cho: Erekana iforoma y’umutwe w’uwo muntu.Tanga inkuru ziryoshe mukoresheje telefone ngendanwa.
